      • validate

        boolean validate(ObjectFrame value,
                 List<String> validationMessages)
        Validates the specified value. Checks whether this object parameter would be valid after setting the specified value.

        Any validation messages will be added to the specified list. If the list is null, no validation messages will be collected.

        Parameters:
        value - the value to validate
        validationMessages - the list of validation messages. May be null.
        Returns:
        true if this object parameter would be valid after setting the specified value, or false, otherwise
